Package com.camerontec.catalys.server.marketdata.pricestep

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IConfigurableContainer
    An interface for objects that a) contain other objects and b) are constructed from a configuration file (or can be written to a configuration file).
    IPriceStepConfigurable
    Object that can store information about configured price steps.
    IPriceStepTable
    IPriceStepTable defines an interface to a price step table.
    IPriceStepTableContainer
    IPriceStepTableContainer is a container of price step tables.
    IPriceStepTableEntry
    IPriceStepTableEntry is an interface for a single entry in a price step table.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PriceStepConfigurationLoader
    PriceStepConfigurationLoader loads XML configuration data for price step tables.
    PriceStepTable
    PriceStepTable provides an implementation of a price step table.
    PriceStepTableDictionary
    PriceStepTableDictionary is a dictionary of price step tables.
    PriceStepTableEntry
    PriceStepTableEntry is an implementation of a single entry in a price step table.
